properties.flavorText: Self-proclaimed king of Norkos Dungeon. Used dark magic to freeze Raburro Town's water source.
A chameleon-like scale that seems to blend in with its surroundings. Normally these are kept to allow the lizard to hide better from danger.
Someone must have tried very hard to create a natural ecosystem in this dungeon.
There's no possible way to have ice stay cold in a dungeon.
They still make noise, despite how unkind time was to them.
In a town of dwarves, this coin would look very strange.
